trans-unit.source: Defines IDs for built-in **Server Explorer** nodes that represent individual components on a SharePoint site, such as nodes that represent lists, fields, or content types.
trans-unit.target: 定义表示 SharePoint 站点上各个组件的内置服务器资源管理器节点的 ID，例如表示列表、字段或内容类型的节点。

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Explorer.Extensions.ExtensionNodeTypes> values with the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Explorer.ExplorerNodeTypeAttribute> to specify a built-in SharePoint node that you want to extend.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Explorer.Extensions.ExtensionNodeTypes>值与<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Explorer.ExplorerNodeTypeAttribute>指定你想要扩展的内置 SharePoint 节点。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Extend a SharePoint Node in Server Explorer](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-extend-a-sharepoint-node-in-server-explorer.md) and [How to: Add a Custom SharePoint Node to Server Explorer](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-add-a-custom-sharepoint-node-to-server-explorer.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[如何： 扩展服务器资源管理器中的 SharePoint 节点](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-extend-a-sharepoint-node-in-server-explorer.md)和[如何： 向服务器资源管理器中添加自定义 SharePoint 节点](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-add-a-custom-sharepoint-node-to-server-explorer.md)。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the ID for nodes that represent a <c>Microsoft.SharePoint.SPContentType</c>.
trans-unit.target: 指定表示 <c>Microsoft.SharePoint.SPContentType</c> 的节点的 ID。

trans-unit.source: Specifies the ID for nodes that represent a <c>Microsoft.SharePoint.SPField</c> that is attached to a content type or list.
trans-unit.target: 指定表示附加到内容类型或列表的 <c>Microsoft.SharePoint.SPField</c> 的节点的 ID。
